/**
 * Portum — OpenAI-compatible chat completions gateway.
 *
 * Endpoints:
 *   POST /v1/chat/completions  — route to upstream provider
 *   GET  /health               — basic health check
 *   GET  /health/providers     — per-provider key + reachability check
 *   GET  /stats                — aggregate stats
 *   GET  /audit                — last 50 requests with full detail
 *   GET  /                     — live dashboard (HTML)
